    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Presenting a true automotive masterpiece: a collector-grade vehicle that looks and drives as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. This car has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled garage, shielded from the elements and treated with an obsessive level of care. The exterior boasts a deep, mirror-like finish with zero imperfections, protected by a high-end ceramic coating. Inside, the cabin is a sanctuary of luxury; the premium leather remains supple and aromatic, free from any wear or creasing, while every technological feature functions with precision. Mechanically, this vehicle is beyond reproach, featuring a comprehensive service history and a drive that is both silent and powerful. From the pristine engine bay to the untouched undercarriage, this is an opportunity to own a virtually new car at a fraction of its original prestige. No stories, no excuses\u2014just pure, unadulterated excellence for the discerning buyer who demands the very best.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
